source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_SEQ_00<tab>Something has been bugging Raganher for a while now.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_SEQ_00<tab>コールドハースのラガンハーは、困り果てているようだ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_TODO_00<tab>Survey the designated locations and slay any plague wamouracampae that appear.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_TODO_00<tab><var 28 ((EObj)) F61EA52C01 /var>で見渡して<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F216F301 /var>を討伐

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_000<tab>Oh, you're one of them adventurin' folk. If you're lookin' for work, you came at the right time.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_000<tab>お前さん、冒険者か？
腕に覚えがあるなら、村を助けてもらえんかのう？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_001<tab>You seen any bugs around? Big ones? We've an infestation of wamouracampae, and the damn things reproduce faster than rabbits in heat.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_001<tab>どうやら村のあちこちに、ブラッドグライダーの卵が、
産み付けられておったようでの……。
最近、次々と幼虫が孵化してきよったんじゃ！

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_100_001<tab>Think you could take care of 'em. They're usually hidin' in the bramble.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_100_001<tab>「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61EA52C01 /var>」で辺りを見渡して、
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F216F301 /var>」を探し出し、駆除してくれ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_002<tab>You'd be doin' us a big favor if you got rid of those damn wamouracampae. They're usually hidin' in the bramble.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_002<tab>「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61EA52C01 /var>」で辺りを見渡して、
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F216F301 /var>」を探し出し、駆除してくれ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_010<tab>You got them all? Bless you, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>. Maybe now we can finally grow somethin' on this barren lump of land.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_010<tab>おお……感謝の言葉もない。
この村は見てのとおり、周囲を岩山に囲まれておる。
年がら年中寒風が吹きすさむ、厳しい土地じゃ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_011<tab>It's hard enough as it is up here in the mountains, cold winds blowin' all year round, killin' anythin' what dares sprout out of the earth. Add in those bloody bugs and you got a recipe for disaster.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_011<tab>細々と農業を続けてはいるものの、収穫なんぞ雀の涙……。
あの<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F216F301 /var>が成虫になったら、どうなったことやら。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_012<tab>Not like we have many left to till the land, anyway. With the Garleans snatchin' up anyone fit to lift hoe or dig a hole, soon we'll have no one left.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_012<tab>昔はワシも、傭兵として名を馳せたもんだが、年には勝てん。
若者は皆、帝国に徴兵されてしもうた。
村も人と同じように老いて……死んでいくものなんじゃろうか？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_013<tab>Don't you worry none, though, <var 08 E905 ((lass)) ((lad)) /var>. If these mountains couldn't do us in after all these years, I reckon nothing will.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ901_02857_RAGANHER_000_013<tab>いや、せんない話じゃった。
ありがとうよ、冒険者さん。
